p: Territory of Washington 3rd Judicial District S.S. In District Court holding terms at Seattle. In the matter of the application of William Fox For a writ of Habeas Corpus Comes now the said William Fox and excepts to the sufficiency of the sheriffs return and recieve for he discharge of him the said William Fox because the said return does not show any sufficient reason for the detention of said William Fox in does it show any legal found whatever for said William Fox is unprisionment J. M. Hall Attorney for said William Fox
